# рџ“‹ Prerequisites

Install the following software before starting:

* **Node.js 20.9+** вЂ” Next.js 16 will refuse to start on Node 18. Node 22 LTS is recommended and is also the minimum required by Capacitor.
* Git
* Visual Studio Code
* Android Studio **Otter (2025.2.1) or newer** *(required if you plan to build for Android вЂ” Capacitor 8 will not work correctly on older Android Studio releases)*

Verify your installation:

```bash
node -v
npm -v
git --version
```

> If `node -v` prints anything below `v20.9.0`, install Node 22 LTS first (e.g. via `nvm install 22 && nvm use 22`).

