# Phase 3 вЂ” Initialize shadcn/ui

The shadcn CLI is now on **v4**, which scaffolds via `--template`, `--base` (component primitives), and `--preset` (design tokens) flags rather than the old fully-interactive-only flow.

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

When prompted, choose:

```text
Template:
вњ” Next.js

Base (primitives):
вњ” Radix

Preset:
вњ” Nova
```

Equivalent non-interactive command:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init -t next -b radix -p nova
```

> `npx shadcn@latest init -d` uses the CLI's own defaults (`--template=next --preset=nova`) if you don't need to pin the base explicitly.

